track locusSpec
superTrack on
shortLabel Locus-specific
longLabel Locus-specific annotations
group genes
visibility hide

    track mucinsNonVntr
    parent locusSpec
    shortLabel Mucin non-VNTR exons
    longLabel Mucin gene non-VNTR exons (Plender et al. 2024 supplementary data)
    type bigGenePred
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/locusSpec/mucins/mucinsNonVntr.bb
    itemRgb on
    visibility pack
    searchIndex name,name2,geneName
    labelFields name,name2,geneName,geneName2
    defaultLabelFields name
    mouseOver <b>$name2 $name</b><br>transcript: $geneName<br>type: $type<br>length: ${chromEnd}-${chromStart}
    priority 2

    track mucinsVntr
    parent locusSpec
    shortLabel Mucin VNTR exons
    longLabel Mucin gene VNTR exons (Plender et al. 2024 supplementary data)
    type bigGenePred
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/locusSpec/mucins/mucinsVntr.bb
    itemRgb on
    visibility pack
    searchIndex name,name2,geneName
    labelFields name,name2,geneName,geneName2
    defaultLabelFields name
    mouseOver <b>$name2 $name</b><br>transcript: $geneName<br>type: $type<br>length: ${chromEnd}-${chromStart}
    priority 1
